From: nick@quay.ie (Nick Hilliard)
Subject: Re: Man pages for tar?
Date: Sat, 11 Sep 1993 15:55:53 GMT

Klaus ZLOEBL (zloebl@piis10.joanneum.ac.at) wrote:

: the man pages for tar are messed up.
: in SLS 1.02 as in SLS 1.03.
: how can i fix it, or where from do i get new ones?

There is no man page for GNU tar at the moment.  If you read the
documentation that comes with the package, it says that there will be one
included with the next release.  If you're really stuck, get the man page
from another unix system.  The main functions (at least) are the same.

